* Care of horses that no longer run the Palio (due to age or injury) at the Equestrian Center of State Forestry, "The Caggio", in the town of [[拉迪孔多利|Radicondoli]].<ref>[http://www.sanpaolo.org/fc05/0533fc/0533fc48.htm Campioni al pascolo, di Gianni Perotti] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sanpaolo.org/fc05/0533fc/0533fc48.htm |date=20110724082904 }} – {{tsl|en|Famiglia Cristiana||Famiglia Cristiana}} page 33 14 August 2005  [http://www.cosedipalio.altervista.org/il.htm questo reportage] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20050120232336/http://www.cosedipalio.altervista.org/il.htm |date=2005-01-20 }} The Breeding Center of wilderness.</ref>
